ures/best-games-2018-red-dead-redemption-2/|archivedate=December 21, 2018|accessdate=August 7, 2019}}</ref> ''[[USgamer]]'',<ref name=\"USgamer\">{{cite web|url=https://www.usgamer.net/articles/usg-top-20-games-of-the-year|title=USG's Top 20 Games of 2018|date=December 28, 2018|work=USgamer|publisher=[[Gamer Network]]|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221041525/https://www.usgamer.net/articles/usg-top-20-games-of-the-year|archivedate=December 21, 2018|accessdate=August 7, 2019}}</ref> and ''[[Vulture (website)|Vulture]]'';<ref name=\"Vulture\">{{cite web|url=https://www.vulture.com/article/best-video-games-2018.html|title=The 10 Best Video Games of 2018|last=Swearingen|first=Jake|date=December 7, 2018|work=Vulture|publisher=[[New York (magazine)|New York Media]]|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181228114245/https://www.vulture.com/article/best-video-games-2018.html|archivedate=December 28, 2018|accessdate=August 7, 2019}}</ref> it was named runner-up by several other publications.<ref name=\"IGN GOTY\"/><ref name=\"GamesRadar\">{{cite web|url=https://www.gamesradar.com/best-games-2018/3/|title=The best games of 2018|date=December 21, 2018|work=[[GamesRadar+]]|publisher=[[Future plc]]|page=3|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225023334/https://www.gamesradar.com/best-games-2018/3/|archivedate=December 25, 2018|accessdate=August 7, 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"Polygon\">{{cite web|url=https://www.polygon.com/2018/5/29/17386324/best-games-2018-ps4-pc-xbox-one|title=Best games of 2018: The top 50 games of the year|date=December 21, 2018|work=[[Polygon (website)|Polygon]]|publisher=[[Vox Media]]|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180529203742/https://www.polygon.com/2018/5/29/17386324/best-games-2018-ps4-pc-xbox-one|archivedate=May 29, 2018|accessdate=August 7, 2019}}</ref>\n\n{{-}}\n\n== Accolades ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"font-size: 95%; width: 